Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初有声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言即是他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人从他言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向其跪拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈地上之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为虚荣与傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡诈与垄断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筑塔如林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲试比天高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揽大地之富
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散人心于荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 对「他之声」充耳不闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他赐人悔过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炽焰伴烟 如狮吼降临大地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众塔归土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾祸离去 却未自省者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今闻圣言 皆同行之真见证者也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地赐其居住者回报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿人挣脱原罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成荣光与尊严之眷族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}当地时间2月26日下午3点30分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}中国 上海浦东新区的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}上海金融中心大厦 遭到爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}爆炸造成大厦全毁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}倒下楼体对连带周边建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}产生多米诺骨牌效应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}至少6栋超高层大厦倒塌 周边设施普遍被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}现场到处是大楼倒塌造成粉尘还伴有火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}当地警察及解放军正全力营救伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}情况暂时可能难有好转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}伤亡人数仍不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}但据报道 至少有一万人以上罹难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}中国政府宣称
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}「这是一场明显的恐怖袭击」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}上海现已处于高度戒严态势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}政府切断了所有出入上海的交通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}据怀疑本次爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}是继美国芝加哥威利斯大厦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}西雅图大型购物中心等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}1.16恐怖袭击爆炸案以来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}世界各地频发的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}「高层大厦连环爆炸案」中的一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}作案动机目的仍旧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\i1}也未有组织声称对其负责
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定 很早就开始策划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抢先了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈 不用给我准备晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是约会呢
